<br>
Fixation of Ro:  Lowers ATK of mob (no more double hits for 400, maybe double hits for 300 but heck that's still 200 hp's less per hit)<br>
<br>
Ro's Fiery Saundering:  Lowers AC and Fire Resistances (more damager for the buck and the Fire Resistance is lowered so much that Imps in Sol B can even be casted on with Fire based DD's after being applied)<br>
<br>
Don't know if this would help any, but I never see druids using these new spells.  Maybe due to their rarity.<br>
