<br>
FLAME ARC<br>
Level: 39<br>
Mana: 199<br>
Cast Time: 5.3 sec<br>
Recast Time: 7 sec<br>
Damage: 171-181<br>
<br>
I know it's not much, but you could put it in-between your cycles of scintillation to up your damage output, instead of just waiting for your spell to recycle.  I have a long way to go before I use this tactic, just asking out of curiosity. <p>--------------------------<BR>
